Summary: Properties for the SkeletonModification2DLookAt class.

Properties:
* bone2d_node (NodePath): Path to the Bone2D node to use for looking at the target. Default: ""
* bone_index (int): Index of the bone to use for looking at the target. Default: -1
* target_nodepath (NodePath): Path to the target node to look at. Default: ""
