Summary: Describes the properties of the SkeletonModification2DLookAt class, which controls a bone's orientation towards a target.

Property Descriptions

Property: bone2d_node (NodePath)
Description: The Bone2D node that the modification will operate on.
Setters: set_bone2d_node(value: NodePath)
Getters: get_bone2d_node() → NodePath
Default: NodePath("")

Property: bone_index (int)
Description: The index of the Bone2D node that the modification will operate on.
Setters: set_bone_index(value: int)
Getters: get_bone_index() → int
Default: -1

Property: target_nodepath (NodePath)
Description: The NodePath to the node that is the target for the LookAt modification. This node is what the modification will rotate the Bone2D to.
Setters: set_target_node(value: NodePath)
Getters: get_target_node() → NodePath
Default: NodePath("")
